#

Bellini

5 min
$15
150 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVegan

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Beverage

Tags:

CocktailBrunchFruity

Description

A refreshing and fruity cocktail made with peach puree and sparkling wine, perfect for brunch or a special occasion.

Ingredients

  • fresh peaches or peach puree: 2 ripe peaches or 1 cup puree
  • prosecco or sparkling wine: 1 bottle (750ml)
  • sugar (optional): 1-2 tablespoons
